{"tid":1694834,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警員遭不知名人士扔汽油彈  臉部嚴重灼傷","createTime":"2019-11-05T10:02:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T12:30:17.000Z","uid":184679,"like":24,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"6f96d63a7f6ec1b3623360db32b8a6392a568504","tid":1694834,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T10:02:39.000Z","msg":"南美洲智利的反政府示威持續上演，昨天群眾再度聚集首都聖地牙哥街頭，跟鎮曓警察爆發衝突。有員警在執勤時，被不知名人士扔擲瓶裝汽油彈，身體當場著火，場面怵目驚心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Y_bbTBA5ux4etlmdfX2dhA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/ftvn.com.tw/edbb4c972a598a24a28f997d2e8af681\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FY_bbTBA5ux4etlmdfX2dhA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fftvn.com.tw%2Fedbb4c972a598a24a28f997d2e8af681&h=9c98cded&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當地反政府示威持續上演，4日，一群全副武裝的員警在執行公務時，突然遭不知名人士扔擲瓶裝汽油彈，導致員警身體當場著火、臉部嚴重灼傷，目前還在加護病房接受治療。不過民眾的怒火，似乎沒有就此平息。<br />\n<br />\n有示威者說：「整個政府系統都有問題，我們正進行抗爭，尤其是我們智利的新自由主義系統。」<br />\n<br />\n也有智利示威者強調：「我認為政府和其他掌權人士，智利示威者必須了解人民的不滿，由於一個國家的不平等待遇，到最後我們都卡在這裡。」<br />\n<br />\n智利由於貧富懸殊等社會跟經濟問題日益嚴重，再加上當局還想漲地鐵票價，讓小老百姓怒火中燒。10月中旬以來，街頭抗爭不斷，不僅讓國家一度陷入緊急狀態，連原本要在智利舉辦的APEC跟聯合國氣候大會，也被迫喊卡。當局現在甚至下調今年的經濟增長預期，從原本的2.6%減到2到2.2%。<br />\n<br />\n4日，民眾再度走上首都聖地牙哥街頭，與鎮暴警察爆發衝突，逼得警方再次搬出水砲車跟催淚彈進行驅離，街頭秒變戰場。這股反政府浪潮究竟何時才會落幕，還沒人說的準。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%99%BA%E5%88%A9%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E5%BB%B6%E7%87%92-%E5%93%A1%E8%AD%A6%E9%81%AD%E4%B8%8D%E7%9F%A5%E5%90%8D%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E6%89%94%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88-%E8%87%89%E9%83%A8%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E7%81%BC%E5%82%B7-091839538.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%2599%25BA%25E5%2588%25A9%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E5%25BB%25B6%25E7%2587%2592-%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%2581%25AD%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%259F%25A5%25E5%2590%258D%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E6%2589%2594%25E6%25B1%25BD%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E5%25BD%2588-%25E8%2587%2589%25E9%2583%25A8%25E5%259A%25B4%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%2581%25BC%25E5%2582%25B7-091839538.html&d=kDaEa4B9Gv5qH72Sa3%2FdwPno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=eb2db182\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%99%BA%E5%88%A9%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E5%BB%B6%E7%87%92-%E5%93%A1%E8%AD%A6%E9%81%AD%E4%B8%8D%E7%9F%A5%E5%90%8D%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E6%89%94%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88-%E8%87%89%E9%83%A8%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E7%81%BC%E5%82%B7-091839538.html</a>"},{"pid":"4a3ab72bb5bf1e84d81c2f864e85aa00012675fe","tid":1694834,"uid":193233,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T10:03:57.000Z","msg":"開心左一陣"},{"pid":"4af99cf2ff38073af49b61bce8c5873e720821b9","tid":1694834,"uid":201464,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a3ab72bb5bf1e84d81c2f864e85aa00012675fe","tid":1694834,"uid":193233,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T10:03:57.000Z","msg":"開心左一陣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T10:05:32.000Z","msg":"+1"},{"pid":"db5f717303aa0948ecba016d84f07131302dbeb9","tid":1694834,"uid":1781,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a3ab72bb5bf1e84d81c2f864e85aa00012675fe","tid":1694834,"uid":193233,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T10:03:57.000Z","msg":"開心左一陣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T10:05:42.000Z","msg":"Same here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"344978c23b64ea8cb2db242a8975b012a3c8cf25","tid":1694834,"uid":124180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T10:07:16.000Z","msg":"又氹人開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34349c921606b790288d6be4bc4a7ec4f07f0842","tid":1694834,"uid":226959,"like":1,"d