n智利由於貧富懸殊等社會跟經濟問題日益嚴重，再加上當局還想漲地鐵票價，讓小老百姓怒火中燒。10月中旬以來，街頭抗爭不斷，不僅讓國家一度陷入緊急狀態，連原本要在智利舉辦的APEC跟聯合國氣候大會，也被迫喊卡。當局現在甚至下調今年的經濟增長預期，從原本的2.6%減到2到2.2%。<br />\n<br />\n4日，民眾再度走上首都聖地牙哥街頭，與鎮暴警察爆發衝突，逼得警方再次搬出水砲車跟催淚彈進行驅離，街頭秒變戰場。這股反政府浪潮究竟何時才會落幕，還沒人說的準。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%99%BA%E5%88%A9%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E5%BB%B6%E7%87%92-%E5%93%A1%E8%AD%A6%E9%81%AD%E4%B8%8D%E7%9F%A5%E5%90%8D%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E6%89%94%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88-%E8%87%89%E9%83%A8%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E7%81%BC%E5%82%B7-091839538.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%2599%25BA%25E5%2588%25A9%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E5%25BB%25B6%25E7%2587%2592-%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%2581%25AD%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%259F%25A5%25E5%2590%258D%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E6%2589%2594%25E6%25B1%25BD%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E5%25BD%2588-%25E8%2587%2589%25E9%2583%25A8%25E5%259A%25B4%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%2581%25BC%25E5%2582%25B7-091839538.html&d=kDaEa4B9Gv5qH72Sa3%2FdwPno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=eb2db182\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%99%BA%E5%88%A9%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E5%BB%B6%E7%87%92-%E5%93%A1%E8%AD%A6%E9%81%AD%E4%B8%8D%E7%9F%A5%E5%90%8D%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E6%89%94%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88-%E8%87%89%E9%83%A8%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E7%81%BC%E5%82%B7-091839538.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T10:37:35.000Z","msg":"香港人做奴隸吧！"},{"pid":"5d2fe06868a855e5951b939a9867af30a9c4b748","tid":1694834,"uid":209390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T10:38:45.000Z","msg":"標題黨搞到我j左半秒"},{"pid":"b38c7ebf6a7dceda09a308b28036a4c9e8c1b213","tid":1694834,"uid":153100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T10:40:51.000Z","msg":"又黎啦又黎啦<br />\n藍絲望下啦<br />\n香港人都比一支野飛落你面到呀"},{"pid":"6da907f0f7cfc87605703f835d5b5e63470397ab","tid":1694834,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5eed1509380f3cf79f52250891f3d06168bbf482","tid":1694834,"uid":34927,"like":1,